snippet.title: Windjammers PS4 / PS Vita - Announcement trailer PSX 2016
snippet.description:
Windjammers, one of the greatest “versus” games of all-time is back with online multiplayer!

Windjammers is a fast-paced head-to-head arcade game where two players face off on a court, and throw discs at the opponent's goal zone to score points. The player with the most points wins. Incredibly fun and intensely addictive, Windjammers is the adrenaline rush you’re looking for!

Originally released on the NEOGEO arcade system, Windjammers perfectly blends sports and fighting games. Sharpen your throwing and sliding skills, use the best techniques to defeat your opponents, and become the world’s best player!
